#
# TURN ORDER
# 1. A stage-based dilemma appears.
# 2. Draw one card from a standard 52-card deck.
# 3. Choose one plant card:
#       Switchgrass / Poplar Trees / Corn Stover
# 4. Resolve tree gain or loss.
# 5. After all dilemmas for the turn, roll the production die.
